{"word":"συγκατακλίνω","slug":"συγκατακλίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συγκατακλίνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-κλῐνῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to make to lie with</i>: — <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to lie together</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, also, <i>to lie on the same couch with</i> another <i>at table</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}